entries.bar_foil1_rand_7: You're making me mad. Anyone got a blaster handy?
entries.bar_foil1_rand_6: Give me my money! This business ain't run on hand-outs!
entries.bar_foil1_rand_5: Someone call the authorities. Or better yet, just shoot this good for nothing stunted Wookiee!
entries.bar_foil1_rand_4: You ordered the drink, you pay for it!
entries.bar_foil1_rand_2: You're not getting away from me. Stop running and pay up!
entries.bar_foil1_rand_1: This little twerp stiffed me! Someone stop him!
entries.cantina_zone_emote: Four Ewoks walk into a cantina...
entries.bar_line_11: Hey you're not leaving without paying!
entries.bar_line_9: What, too strong for ya? Well it's 25 credits anyway so pay up.
entries.bar_line_6: That? You want one of those? Ok here you go.
entries.bar_line_4: Umm, look behind me. That's what we have to offer. And could you tell your friends to quit running all over the place, it's really distracting.
entries.bar_line_2: What? I don't understand your language but I assume you're here for a drink.
entries.foil1_finally: Finally! Thanks for taking care of those beasts. What a mess!
entries.foil1_rand_7: That's sensitive equipment! Somebody stop these wretches!
entries.foil1_rand_6: Stop right where you are you little beast and give that back to me!
entries.foil1_rand_5: Stop trying to eat my datapad and give it back!
entries.foil1_rand_4: Give that back! Anyone have a blaster on them?
entries.foil1_rand_2: Hey, you can't eat that! Stop biting it and give it back to me!
entries.foil1_rand_1: Give that back you little thief!
entries.foil1_10: Hey give that back you little monster!
entries.foil1_6: Hey get your grubby little hands off me!
